# The README.md for the plugin is copied from root during prepublishOnly script
plugin/README.md

# The Rokt kits are metadata-only Cordova wrappers with no npm dependencies, so
# they carry no package-lock.json. These are ignored to stop an empty/spurious
# lock from being committed (and bumped by the release workflow's `npm version`).
# When a kit first gains a real npm dependency, remove its line below and commit
# the regenerated lock — plus a CI job that runs `npm ci` against the kit.
# NOTE: plugin/package-lock.json is intentionally NOT ignored; it is tracked and
# enforced by the JS Tests CI job.
Kits/Rokt/package-lock.json
Kits/RoktPaymentExtension/package-lock.json
